    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In a Zend_Db_Table object:</p>

<p>$this-&gt;select()-&gt;limit(0,4)-&gt;__toString();</p>

<p>Will give you</p>

<p>SELECT <code>table</code>.* FROM <code>table</code> LIMIT 9223372036854775807 OFFSET 10</p>

<p>for both pdo_mysql and mysqli adapters. Values of one and above work as expected.</p>

